        <item>
          <title>No. 5 UConn claims 5th straight Big East regular-season title with 72-53 win over No. 22 Creighton</title>
          <description><![CDATA[HARTFORD, Conn. (AP) — Sarah Strong had 22 points and nine rebounds and Paige Bueckers added 15 points, seven rebounds and seven assists as No. 5 UConn defeated No. 22 Creighton 72-53 on Thursday night and claimed its fifth straight Big East regular-season title.]]></description>
