          <title>An ex-minor league catcher was accused of trying to lose on purpose. He says he didn't tip pitches</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A former minor league catcher in the Minnesota Twins organization who was released last year, reportedly because he tried to make sure his team would lose so the season would end, denied the allegation in an interview with The Athletic and said he didn't tip any pitches to his opponents.]]></description>
